## Tested Scenarios

### Success Paths (Happy Path) ✓
- Creating resources with valid data
- Reading existing resources
- Updating resources with valid data
- Deleting resources
- Filtering data (today's menu, active orders)

### Error Handling ✓
- Invalid resource IDs (404 Not Found)
- Invalid request data (400 Bad Request)
- Business rule violations:
  - Non-existent meal IDs
  - Negative portion counts
  - Sold-out items
  - Invalid state transitions

### Business Logic ✓
- Portion count decreases on order creation
- Meal deactivation instead of deletion
- Order state transitions with validation
- Menu filtering by date

